---
layout: base.njk
permalink: /diagnosis.html
title: Self-check
description: "A short, private RCPD symptom self-check based on the recognized symptom pattern. A few questions to see how closely your experience matches no-burp syndrome. Not a diagnosis."
scripts:
  - /assets/js/quiz.js
---

<section class="page-head section section--tight">
  <div class="wrap">
    <p class="eyebrow">Self-check</p>
    <h1>Do my symptoms match RCPD?</h1>
    <p class="lead">
      Six quick questions based on the symptom pattern clinicians associate with RCPD. It takes
      about a minute, and everything stays in your browser &mdash; nothing is sent, stored, or shared.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
  <div class="wrap">
    <form id="quiz" class="quiz" novalidate>
      <div id="quiz-intro">
        <p class="callout callout--note">
          This is an educational self-check, <strong>not a diagnosis</strong>. It can't tell you
          whether you have RCPD &mdash; only a qualified clinician can do that. Use your result as a
          starting point for that conversation.
        </p>
        <button type="button" class="btn btn--primary" id="quiz-start">Start the self-check</button>
      </div>

      <div id="quiz-progress" hidden>
        <div class="progress"><div class="progress__bar" id="progress-bar"></div></div>
        <p class="progress__text" id="progress-text">Question 1 of 6</p>
      </div>

      <div id="quiz-steps" hidden>
        <fieldset class="quiz__q" data-step="1" hidden>
          <legend>1. When you feel the urge to burp, are you unable to &mdash; with nothing coming up, even after fizzy drinks or swallowing air?</legend>
          <p class="quiz__hint">Being unable to burp is the central feature of RCPD.</p>
          <div class="options">
            <label class="option"><input type="radio" name="q1" value="0"> Never &mdash; I burp normally</label>
            <label class="option"><input type="radio" name="q1" value="1"> Rarely</label>
            <label class="option"><input type="radio" name="q1" value="2"> Sometimes</label>
            <label class="option"><input type="radio" name="q1" value="3"> Often</label>
            <label class="option"><input type="radio" name="q1" value="4"> Always &mdash; I can't burp at all</label>
          </div>
        </fieldset>

        <fieldset class="quiz__q" data-step="2" hidden>
          <legend>2. Do you hear gurgling, croaking, or rumbling noises low in your throat or chest, especially after eating or drinking?</legend>
          <div class="options">
            <label class="option"><input type="radio" name="q2" value="0"> Never</label>
            <label class="option"><input type="radio" name="q2" value="1"> Rarely</label>
            <label class="option"><input type="radio" name="q2" value="2"> Sometimes</label>
            <label class="option"><input type="radio" name="q2" value="3"> Often</label>
            <label class="option"><input type="radio" name="q2" value="4"> Always</label>
          </div>
        </fieldset>

        <fieldset class="quiz__q" data-step="3" hidden>
          <legend>3. Do you get uncomfortable bloating or pressure in your chest or upper abdomen, made worse by carbonation or large meals?</legend>
          <div class="options">
            <label class="option"><input type="radio" name="q3" value="0"> Never</label>
            <label class="option"><input type="radio" name="q3" value="1"> Rarely</label>
            <label class="option"><input type="radio" name="q3" value="2"> Sometimes</label>
            <label class="option"><input type="radio" name="q3" value="3"> Often</label>
            <label class="option"><input type="radio" name="q3" value="4"> Always</label>
          </div>
        </fieldset>

        <fieldset class="quiz__q" data-step="4" hidden>
          <legend>4. Do you pass gas (flatulence) far more than seems normal &mdash; as if air that can't come up has to find its way out the other end?</legend>
          <div class="options">
            <label class="option"><input type="radio" name="q4" value="0"> Never</label>
            <label class="option"><input type="radio" name="q4" value="1"> Rarely</label>
            <label class="option"><input type="radio" name="q4" value="2"> Sometimes</label>
            <label class="option"><input type="radio" name="q4" value="3"> Often</label>
            <label class="option"><input type="radio" name="q4" value="4"> Always</label>
          </div>
        </fieldset>

        <fieldset class="quiz__q" data-step="5" hidden>
          <legend>5. Do you get a &ldquo;stuck air&rdquo; feeling or nausea that's only relieved by lying down, passing gas, or air slowly working its way up your throat?</legend>
          <div class="options">
            <label class="option"><input type="radio" name="q5" value="0"> Never</label>
            <label class="option"><input type="radio" name="q5" value="1"> Rarely</label>
            <label class="option"><input type="radio" name="q5" value="2"> Sometimes</label>
            <label class="option"><input type="radio" name="q5" value="3"> Often</label>
            <label class="option"><input type="radio" name="q5" value="4"> Always</label>
          </div>
        </fieldset>

        <fieldset class="quiz__q" data-step="6" hidden>
          <legend>6. Does not being able to burp affect your daily life &mdash; your eating, social plans, or anxiety levels?</legend>
          <div class="options">
            <label class="option"><input type="radio" name="q6" value="0"> Never</label>
            <label class="option"><input type="radio" name="q6" value="1"> Rarely</label>
            <label class="option"><input type="radio" name="q6" value="2"> Sometimes</label>
            <label class="option"><input type="radio" name="q6" value="3"> Often</label>
            <label class="option"><input type="radio" name="q6" value="4"> Always</label>
          </div>
        </fieldset>

        <div class="quiz__nav">
          <button type="button" class="btn btn--ghost" id="quiz-prev" hidden>Back</button>
          <button type="button" class="btn btn--primary" id="quiz-next" disabled>Next</button>
          <button type="button" class="btn btn--primary" id="quiz-submit" hidden disabled>See my result</button>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div id="quiz-result" class="quiz__result" tabindex="-1" hidden>
        <p class="band" id="result-band"></p>
        <p class="quiz__score" id="result-title"></p>
        <p id="result-text"></p>
        <div class="cluster" style="margin-top:1.2rem">
          <a href="/find-a-doctor.html" class="btn btn--primary">Find a doctor</a>
          <button type="button" class="btn btn--ghost" id="quiz-restart">Start over</button>
        </div>
        <p class="figure-note">
          This self-check is for information only and is not a medical diagnosis. RCPD is usually a
          lifelong pattern &mdash; if your symptoms started suddenly or recently, mention that to a
          doctor, as it can point to a different cause.
        </p>
      </div>
    </form>
  </div>
</section>
